# Feature documentation

Human-readable documentation per feature. One folder per feature **slug** (kebab-case).

Unlike formal SPECs (`.work/features/<slug>/`), these docs describe what the feature does, how to use it, and key entry points — no behavioural spec gates required.

**Create for brownfield:** `@feature-spec document - <slug>`
**Create from SPEC:** `@feature-spec document - <slug>` (auto-populates from existing SPEC)
